metadata.name: Unravel People's ODBS
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's ODBS, which represents an inactive state of pODBS. User can participate in a new Otherdeed for Biogenic Swamp acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's ODBS as credit. upODBS can be claimed into pODBS when the subscription successfully acquires a new Otherdeed for Biogenic Swamp.
